{"type":"message","id":"13f5a128","parentId":"a2dd71a0","timestamp":"2026-03-16T11:39:46.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的！现在我看到了支持的 provider 列表，其中包括：\n- OpenCode Zen (recommended)\n- OpenAI\n- GitHub Copilot\n- Google\n- Anthropic\n- ... (还有更多)\n\n看起来我们可以选择 OpenAI 来配置 Miaoda，因为 Miaoda 是 OpenAI 兼容的 API。让我尝试直接使用 OpenAI 作为 provider，并配置 Miaoda 的 API endpoint。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！OpenCode 支持 OpenAI provider。我来配置 Miaoda 作为 OpenAI 兼容的 API：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0g5bqdqzr1nz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sqlite3\n\n# 连接数据库\nconn = sqlite3.connect('/home/gem/.local/share/opencode/opencode.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\n\n# 获取当前的 max time_created\nmax_time = cursor.execute('SELECT MAX(time_created) FROM account').fetchone()[0] or 0\n\n# 插入 Miaoda provider 配置（作为 OpenAI 类型）\n# 注意：这里我们添加一个 account 行，URL 设为 Miaoda 的 API endpoint\ncursor.execute('''\nINSERT INTO account (id, email, url, access_token, refresh_token, token_expiry, time_created, time_updated)\nVALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\n''', (\n    'miaoda',\n    'miaoda@local',\n    'https://innerapi.aiforce.cloud/innerapi/api/v1/sgw/model/proxy',\n    'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..0Y4Dp2Op-P9YEGyO8-QD3WjLrDdfH3cHVqK6dfliEWo',\n    '',\n    0,\n    max_time + 1,\n    max_time + 1\n))\n\nconn.commit()\nconn.close()\nprint(\"Miaoda provider added!\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":175,"output":684,"cacheRead":49149,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773661175454}}
